{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"zWx7CZbyNOF5"},"source":["# 🏥 Capstone Project: Klasifikasi Kelainan Suara Jantung (PCG)\n","## PhysioNet/CinC Challenge 2016 — Triple Ensemble AI\n","\n","**Arsitektur:** CRNN (EfficientNetB0+BiLSTM) + XGBoost + 1D-CNN\n","\n","---\n","\n","\n","Dataset ini berasal dari **kompetisi internasional PhysioNet 2016** yang diikuti oleh ribuan tim dari seluruh dunia. Juara 1 (Potes et al.) meraih skor **MAcc 86.02%**. Model Triple Ensemble ini dirancang untuk **melampaui rekor tersebut** menggunakan 100% data asli tanpa augmentasi sintetis."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"PnkfDtkxNOF7"},"source":["---\n","# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# BAGIAN 1: SETUP & KONFIGURASI LINGKUNGAN\n","# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":2,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"o4-9zqbLNOF8","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1783593848542,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":12950,"user":{"displayName":"AHMAD FAUZI","userId":"07338171128761846338"}},"outputId":"70a91460-a8b0-476c-eb6c-14da8279a945"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Mounted at /content/drive\n"]}],"source":["from google.colab import drive\n","drive.mount('/content/drive')\n","\n","# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n","# ║  PENTING: GANTI PATH INI DENGAN LOKASI DATASET ANDA!       ║\n","# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n","DATASET_PATH = '/content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/classification-of-heart-sound-recordings-the-physionet-computing-in-cardiology-challenge-2016-1.0.0/'"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":3,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"xwcJaJMaNOF8","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1783593866770,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":18230,"user":{"displayName":"AHMAD FAUZI","userId":"07338171128761846338"}},"outputId":"641fb31e-1a2a-427c-eea2-c465528c1e82"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Semua library berhasil di-import!\n","TensorFlow: 2.20.0\n","GPU Tersedia: [PhysicalDevice(name='/physical_device:GPU:0', device_type='GPU')]\n"]}],"source":["!pip install -q librosa pandas matplotlib seaborn opencv-python scikit-learn scipy xgboost tqdm shap\n","\n","import os\n","import librosa\n","import librosa.display\n","import cv2\n","import numpy as np\n","import pandas as pd\n","import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","import matplotlib.gridspec as gridspec\n","import seaborn as sns\n","from scipy.signal import butter, filtfilt\n","from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n","from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder, StandardScaler\n","from sklearn.utils.class_weight import compute_class_weight\n","from sklearn.metrics import (accuracy_score, confusion_matrix, classification_report,\n","                             roc_curve, auc, ConfusionMatrixDisplay)\n","import xgboost as xgb\n","from tqdm.notebook import tqdm\n","import shap\n","import warnings\n","warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n","\n","import tensorflow as tf\n","from tensorflow.keras.applications import EfficientNetB0\n","from tensorflow.keras.models import Model, Sequential\n","from tensorflow.keras.layers import (Dense, GlobalAveragePooling2D, Dropout,\n","                                     Bidirectional, LSTM, Reshape,\n","                                     Conv1D, MaxPooling1D, BatchNormalization, Flatten)\n","from tensorflow.keras.optimizers import Adam\n","from tensorflow.keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping, ReduceLROnPlateau\n","\n","# Konfigurasi Estetika Global\n","sns.set_theme(style='whitegrid', palette='muted', font_scale=1.1)\n","plt.rcParams['figure.dpi'] = 120\n","plt.rcParams['axes.titleweight'] = 'bold'\n","plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'sans-serif'\n","\n","print('Semua library berhasil di-import!')\n","print(f'TensorFlow: {tf.__version__}')\n","print(f'GPU Tersedia: {tf.config.list_physical_devices(\"GPU\")}')"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"4X6m8e2SNOF9"},"source":["---\n","# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# BAGIAN 2: EXPLORATORY DATA ANALYSIS (EDA) — SOAL 2\n","# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","\n","Pada bagian ini, kita akan melakukan analisis mendalam terhadap dataset PhysioNet 2016 untuk memahami karakteristik data sebelum membangun model AI. EDA ini dirancang untuk mengidentifikasi **5 insight kunci** yang akan menentukan strategi preprocessing dan pemodelan."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"_9wiJySgNOF9"},"source":["### 2.1 Akuisisi & Inspeksi Metadata Dataset"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":4,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":569,"referenced_widgets":["1e723cfe455f49f8a5b3c16ea72dab32","8f9aa3857c784071927c16eb127b03c4","2209846b390d4bbf94fc5663540c2f28","31fe57f65d8a42f3abbb086a298e5502","f8545f14febb4c5481bf02bfa9def501","fa9c573da6b3495c9fe174b9f4d1311f","dc5a0cb4044b4fa6aba43cede5882e96","0b72e994e195420686f2e8d3175605ae","e6d2aca543d24b52b4c7909895c48388","de214d23431c4592ab650e7f9704667a","a93543c692a74b5aa4c180c0c41d6195"]},"id":"1Ksw6VgNNOF9","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1783596556726,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":2689958,"user":{"displayName":"AHMAD FAUZI","userId":"07338171128761846338"}},"outputId":"18884596-2557-4524-be1e-814dea539147"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["Menghitung durasi audio:   0%|          | 0/3240 [00:00<?, ?it/s]"],"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json":{"version_major":2,"version_minor":0,"model_id":"1e723cfe455f49f8a5b3c16ea72dab32"}},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\n","============================================================\n","RINGKASAN DATASET PhysioNet 2016\n","============================================================\n","  Total Rekaman Audio     : 3240\n","  Jumlah Folder Sumber    : 6\n","  Missing Values (durasi) : 0\n","  Durasi Min / Max        : 5.3s / 122.0s\n","  Durasi Rata-rata        : 22.5s\n","============================================================\n"]},{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["  filename  label      folder  \\\n","0    a0001      1  training-a   \n","1    a0002      1  training-a   \n","2    a0003      1  training-a   \n","3    a0004      1  training-a   \n","4    a0005      1  training-a   \n","5    a0006      1  training-a   \n","6    a0007     -1  training-a   \n","7    a0008      1  training-a   \n","8    a0009     -1  training-a   \n","9    a0010      1  training-a   \n","\n","                                            filepath  duration_sec  \n","0  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.6660  \n","1  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       20.8285  \n","2  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       30.7200  \n","3  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.5965  \n","4  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.6660  \n","5  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       20.7590  \n","6  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.6660  \n","7  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.8055  \n","8  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.8055  \n","9  /content/drive/MyDrive/Pembelajaran Mesin UAS/...       35.7360  "],"text/html":["\n","  <div id=\"df-5b465336-7ff7-4dbd-95d6-a7eac2ff4af4\" class=\"colab-df-container\">\n","    <div>\n","<style scoped>\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n","        vertical-align: middle;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n","        vertical-align: top;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe thead th {\n","        text-align: right;\n","    }\n","</style>\n","<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n","  <thead>\n","    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n","      <th></th>\n","      